{"tid":176081,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"無雙☆群星大會串》「柔軟引擎」展示！嬌喘加乳搖太刺激","createTime":"2017-03-28T02:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T02:59:46.000Z","uid":19707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92e346edc02881d0f23a2e99e4bdce6a8769d17b","tid":176081,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"光榮新作《無雙☆群星大會串》近來宣傳連發，遊戲採用了《生死格鬥5》的「柔軟引擎」，除了幾位加入戰鬥的生死格鬥姐姐，其他女性角色也會跟著晃動起來，滿螢幕的福利超乎想象。<br />\n<br />\n正如其名，《無雙群星大會串》中加入了眾多光榮的遊戲角色，徹徹底底的大混鬥，不同畫風不同遊戲的人物強行出現在一個畫面之中。很多玩家熟悉的女性角色，《生死格鬥5》的穗乃果、霞自然不必說，其他妹子也在柔軟引擎的作用下煥發新生，相信會有更多人物在後續的DLC中加入。<br />\n<br />\n無雙群星大會串》即將在3月30日同步發行中文版和日版。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S2-alZVdZfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS2-alZVdZfE&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=40281a12\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S2-alZVdZfE</a>"},{"pid":"e8f81d32d133aa6e5867ede28eaa1591da4ab908","tid":176081,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://pcucgame.com/%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E7%BE%A4%E6%98%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%B2-%E6%9F%94%E8%BB%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpcucgame.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259B%2599%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25B2-%25E6%259F%2594%25E8%25BB%259F%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2593%258E%2F&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ce8d1a36\" target=\"_blank\">https://pcucgame.com/%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E7%BE%A4%E6%98%9F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%B2-%E6%9F%94%E8%BB%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/</a>"}]}